column4: Joseph Abboud Purple Gingham Dress Shirt
column10: In a subtle purple gingham pattern, this fine dress shirt by Joseph Abboud completes your dress, or dress casual look in comfort and crisp style. This fine shirt is tailored from 100% Egyptian cotton and is woven with natural stretch for the best in comfort and fit. A non-iron finish makes this shirt easy care and provides a long lasting polished look. Regular sizes are Modern Fit. Tall sizes are Modern Fit. Big sizes are Classic Fit.
